title: The Lone Rider in Frontier Fury

sources.title: The Lone Rider in Frontier Fury
sources.description: Having been framed and convicted of murder, Tom Cameron (George Houston) heads for Malone's (Karl Hackett) saloon where wanted outlaws hang out. He learns Malone is after the ranch of the man he supposedly killed. When he tries to help the new owner he is captured by Malone's men who plan to hang him. Malone's daughter (Virginia Card) wants to get away from the saloon and hoping Tom will take her, gives him unexpected help.

sources.title: Lone Rider in Frontier Fury (1941) GEORGE HOUSTON
sources.description:
Stars: George Houston, Al St. John, Hillary Brooke
 Director: Sam Newfield

 A cowboy is falsely accused of the murder of a local rancher.
